Package it.emarolab.scene_identification_tracking.semanticSceneLibrary.objects

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Array3D.SemanticMap<D extends Semantics.Descriptor>
    The generic interface to define the mapping of a 3D array in a semantic structure.
    Array3D.SemanticMap.Resources<D extends Semantics.Descriptor,T>
    The base interface for specifying the specific semantic of a 3D array to be mapped from the Array3D.SemanticMap.
    Semantics
    General interface to define the mapping between an object and the semantics structure.
    Semantics.Cone<D extends Semantics.Descriptor>
    This interface represents the class that should describe a Cone like object.
    Semantics.Cylinder<D extends Semantics.Descriptor>
    This interface represents the class that should describe a Cylinder like object.
    Semantics.Descriptor<O,I>
    This interface represents the class that should be able to manage a specific semantic description ( e.g.: XML, OWL, MongoDB etc...).
    Semantics.Logger
    Defines common function for debugging and logging.
    Semantics.Orientable<D extends Semantics.Descriptor>
    This interface represents the class that should describe an orientable object.
    Semantics.Plane<D extends Semantics.Descriptor>
    This interface represents the class that should describe a planar object.
    Semantics.Primitive<D extends Semantics.Descriptor>
    This interface represents the class that should describe a primitive object.
    Semantics.Sphere<D extends Semantics.Descriptor>
    This interface represents the class that should describe a spherical object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Array3D
    Represents an easy ontological mapping structure of a spatial 3D array.
    Semantics.Base
    Defines common function for debugging and logging.
    Semantics.MappingState
    This class implements the possible common states between reading (Semantics.ReadingState) and writing (Semantics.WritingState) to/from semantic operation.
    Semantics.MappingTry<Y extends Semantics.MappingState>  
    Semantics.ReadingOutcome<T>
    A container for reading results.
    Semantics.ReadingState
    This class implements the possible state for a semantic reading process.
    Semantics.Try<Y>
    This is an helper to manage Semantics.MappingState.ERROR states for reading and writing operations.
    Semantics.TryingRead
    The Semantics.MappingTry implementation for reading operations.
    Semantics.TryingWrite
    The Semantics.MappingTry implementation for writing operations.
    Semantics.WritingState
    This class implements the possible state for a semantic writing process.
